Guest space in kintone
 >Guest Space] is a space where non-users of [kintone] can join as a guest. It can be used as a communication space for joint projects with members outside the company.
 >In the guest space, you can send an invitation email to your guests. Invited guests can access kintone from the invitation email and create a guest account.
 >Guests can only access the space to which they have been invited and the applications belonging to that space. Other data cannot be viewed.
		[Guest Space - kintone help https://jp.cybozu.help/k/ja/user/guest.html]
